no.ntnu.fp.gui
Class PersonListModel

java.lang.Object
  javax.swing.AbstractListModel
      no.ntnu.fp.gui.PersonListModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.beans.PropertyChangeListener, java.io.Serializable, java.util.EventListener, javax.swing.ListModel
 class PersonListModel
extends javax.swing.AbstractListModel
implements java.beans.PropertyChangeListener

A ListModel implementation that wraps a Project object. Makes it possible to directly view the Project's contained Persons in a JList. It extends AbstractListModel, to inherit support for listeners and firing events.
